Fine. Have him get back to me.

15:03.880 --> 15:05.910
He's avoiding my calls, Alan.

15:05.930 --> 15:07.000
I'm gonna die.

15:07.030 --> 15:09.030
No. No you're not.

15:09.040 --> 15:11.140
I can feel it.

15:11.170 --> 15:14.780
You might as well just drive
into that tree and kill us both.

15:14.790 --> 15:19.080
Sure. I don't want to
go on living without you.

15:20.120 --> 15:22.370
What's the point of it all?

15:22.380 --> 15:26.840
Yeah, I'm rich, charming,
classically handsome.

15:26.850 --> 15:31.950
I've laid more pipe than a
guy who has sex with pipes.

15:32.810 --> 15:36.120
But what have I done with my life?

15:36.130 --> 15:41.150
A few stupid jingles; some kids'
songs-- nothing that really matters.

15:41.160 --> 15:45.020
Now, now, you're being
too hard on yourself.

15:45.030 --> 15:48.160
I've got no wife,
I've got no children...

15:48.180 --> 15:50.520
I'm going leave this
world the way I came in...

15:50.560 --> 15:53.640
By Cesarean section?

15:53.930 --> 15:56.150
Alone.

15:56.160 --> 16:00.010
Oh, for God sakes, Charlie, I
am tired of listening to this.

16:00.040 --> 16:05.940
There has always been one person in your life who's
been there for you and loved you unconditionally.

16:08.100 --> 16:10.180
You mean...

16:12.990 --> 16:14.570
You're right.

16:14.580 --> 16:16.590
How could I have missed it?

16:16.600 --> 16:18.230
It's been in front of me the whole time!

16:18.250 --> 16:20.570
Well, you know, sometimes you
can't see the forest for the trees,

16:20.600 --> 16:23.470
even when the forest
is in your own backyard.

16:23.510 --> 16:26.110
Or guest room.

16:26.520 --> 16:29.500
Rose?

16:30.070 --> 16:32.400
Yep, the one and only.

16:32.410 --> 16:35.520
I know, I know. It's been awhile.

16:36.180 --> 16:41.240
I was thinking, if you're not too busy, maybe
we can get together, have a drink or something?

16:41.250 --> 16:42.960
Well, great!

16:42.990 --> 16:46.130
So, do you want to meet,
or should I pick you up?

16:53.720 --> 16:57.100
Okay, I'll meet you back at my place.

16:59.970 --> 17:01.820
Small world.

17:01.830 --> 17:05.380
Yeah. Teeny-tiny.

17:09.849 --> 17:13.040
- Here you go.
- Thank you, Charlie.

17:13.050 --> 17:15.440
- You comfy?
- Oh, very.

17:15.450 --> 17:17.210
Good.

17:20.849 --> 17:22.880
So, Rose...

17:22.900 --> 17:24.930
Charlie...

17:24.940 --> 17:26.430
Haven't seen you in awhile.

17:26.460 --> 17:29.110
Can't say the same.

17:30.700 --> 17:32.780
Right, uh, sure.

17:32.790 --> 17:34.870
Sorry about your friend.

17:34.880 --> 17:38.950
Yeah, yeah, it was a
real wake-up call for me.

17:38.970 --> 17:41.370
I can imagine.

17:41.390 --> 17:44.700
Makes you stop and wonder
what's important in your life.

17:44.710 --> 17:47.320
Who's important in your life.

17:47.350 --> 17:50.290
I've always known who's
important in my life.

17:50.300 --> 17:53.330
You have, haven't you.

17:53.930 --> 17:57.230
You know how I feel about you, right?

17:57.250 --> 18:00.350
Tell me anyway.

18:00.360 --> 18:02.410
Oh, okay.

18:02.420 --> 18:05.990
